  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Fight back the darkness with the maidens!”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The conventional objective of the classic Minesweeper game is to pinpoint every instance of a mine(darkness) in the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become friends with the maidens, and depending on the relationship, they will either reveal safe tiles or seal darkness tiles for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · 10 different maidens with unique skills to assist you throughout every game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · The more you interact with a maiden, the better the relationship becomes, and her skill will become more powerful and useful to you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · Customizable difficulty and a leaderboard that saves your best results</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · Some secrets about the maidens' backstory await discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Darkness has come and is trying to consume everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But what if, the maidens wonder, the Darkness just wants to be friends with us?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(✿˶◕‿◕˶)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >____________________________________________________________________</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a mini-project by a solo developer, feel free to join the Discord and share your thoughts</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Fight back the darkness with the maidens!”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The conventional objective of the classic Minesweeper game is to pinpoint every instance of a mine(darkness) in the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become friends with the maidens, and depending on the relationship, they will either reveal safe tiles or seal darkness tiles for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · 10 different maidens with unique skills to assist you throughout every game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · The more you interact with a maiden, the better the relationship becomes, and her skill will become more powerful and useful to you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · Customizable difficulty and a leaderboard that saves your best results</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · Some secrets about the maidens' backstory await discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Darkness has come and is trying to consume everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But what if, the maidens wonder, the Darkness just wants to be friends with us?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(✿˶◕‿◕˶)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >____________________________________________________________________</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a mini-project by a solo developer, feel free to join the Discord and share your thoughts</p>",
